WEBVTT

00:02:42.529 --> 00:02:44.597
Oh I thank you very much,

00:02:44.831 --> 00:02:46.900
all of you, for coming.

00:03:58.204 --> 00:04:02.141
Mayor of Cincinnati

00:04:02.208 --> 00:04:05.144
has declared today

00:04:05.211 --> 00:04:08.514
as "Shri Mataji Day" in Cincinnati.

00:04:18.191 --> 00:04:21.194
And I will read this proclamation

00:04:21.261 --> 00:04:23.696
which I am very thrilled about because,

00:04:23.696 --> 00:04:25.698
somebody would know that

00:04:25.798 --> 00:04:27.600
Shri Mataji is an international figure.

00:04:28.401 --> 00:04:30.403
She is a diplomat.

00:04:30.403 --> 00:04:34.007
Her husband has been the Secretary General

00:04:34.707 --> 00:04:38.711
of a very large United Nations
organization.

00:04:39.779 --> 00:04:42.515
He has been knighted by the Queen of England.

00:04:42.749 --> 00:04:46.185
He has received the highest awards

00:04:46.719 --> 00:04:49.355
from many, many nations

00:04:49.622 --> 00:04:51.190
and he is

00:04:51.190 --> 00:04:53.993
one of the living legends in the world today.

00:04:54.260 --> 00:04:57.030
His name is Sir C.P. Shrivastava

00:04:57.030 --> 00:04:58.798
and Shri Mataji, herself,

00:04:58.798 --> 00:05:01.801
has been honored, all over the world.

00:05:02.902 --> 00:05:05.905
And it's my pleasure to read this proclamation.

00:05:06.639 --> 00:05:09.075
It says: "We proclaim

00:05:09.075 --> 00:05:10.610
whereas

00:05:10.610 --> 00:05:13.613
Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi, "The Mother,"

00:05:14.247 --> 00:05:16.883
is recognized internationally

00:05:16.883 --> 00:05:21.087
as the most significant spiritual force
in the world today.

00:05:22.055 --> 00:05:24.324
And she will awaken in us

00:05:24.324 --> 00:05:28.194
the force that will change our lives
and that change the world.

00:05:29.595 --> 00:05:31.497
And whereas,

00:05:31.497 --> 00:05:33.766
The United Nations honor her

00:05:33.766 --> 00:05:35.735
with a U.N. Peace Medal.

00:05:36.302 --> 00:05:40.039
And whereas, Shri Mataji has developed

00:05:40.606 --> 00:05:43.042
A simple meditation technique,

00:05:43.042 --> 00:05:44.944
"Sahaja Yoga"

00:05:44.944 --> 00:05:47.480
which enables the en masse

00:05:47.747 --> 00:05:50.016
experience of self-realization.

00:05:50.583 --> 00:05:53.453
Breakthrough of the new awareness.

00:05:53.453 --> 00:05:54.787
And whereas,

00:05:54.787 --> 00:05:56.956
Sahaja Yoga

00:05:56.956 --> 00:06:00.059
is the next evolutionary step
for humanity

00:06:00.860 --> 00:06:04.230
which can bring the transformation
of human consciousness

00:06:04.597 --> 00:06:06.666
to a higher level.

00:06:06.666 --> 00:06:09.669
And whereas, the city of Cincinnati,

00:06:09.669 --> 00:06:11.404
is honored

00:06:11.404 --> 00:06:14.407
by the visit of Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi

00:06:14.607 --> 00:06:17.610
who will introduce through Sahaja Yoga

00:06:17.877 --> 00:06:20.880
the experience of harmonious well-being,

00:06:21.614 --> 00:06:23.916
and inner transformation

00:06:23.916 --> 00:06:26.919
that can lead us out of the confusion and frustration

00:06:26.919 --> 00:06:28.788
of modern living

00:06:28.788 --> 00:06:33.192
and spark the greatest inner transformation yet seen.

00:06:33.993 --> 00:06:35.495
Now therefore,

00:06:35.495 --> 00:06:38.498
I, Dwight Tillery, mayor of the City of Cincinnati

00:06:39.198 --> 00:06:44.637
do hereby proclaim Thursday, September 10th, 1992,

00:06:45.538 --> 00:06:50.643
as "Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi Day,"
in Cincinnati.

00:07:17.737 --> 00:07:20.840
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:07:31.350 --> 00:07:34.053
At the very outset

00:07:34.053 --> 00:07:36.122
we have to know

00:07:36.122 --> 00:07:39.125
that truth is what it is.

00:07:39.525 --> 00:07:42.261
We cannot change it.

00:07:42.261 --> 00:07:43.996
We cannot

00:07:43.996 --> 00:07:46.732
conceptualize it.

00:07:46.732 --> 00:07:50.736
Unfortunately, at this human level,

00:07:51.304 --> 00:07:54.307
we cannot feel it.

00:07:54.874 --> 00:07:57.710
We have to become

00:07:57.710 --> 00:08:00.713
something more.

00:08:02.715 --> 00:08:05.718
Unless and until

00:08:06.319 --> 00:08:09.322
that happens to us

00:08:09.322 --> 00:08:11.557
we cannot know the truth.

00:08:11.557 --> 00:08:14.560
The absolute truth.

00:08:15.428 --> 00:08:18.397
I call you all as seekers of truth.

00:08:20.233 --> 00:08:23.236
And if you are seekers of truth,

00:08:24.270 --> 00:08:27.273
you have to open your mind like scientists

00:08:28.040 --> 00:08:31.410
and treat
whatever I'm telling you as a hypothesis.

00:08:32.378 --> 00:08:38.317
And if it works, you should accept
and grow in it.

00:08:39.452 --> 00:08:42.722
You have been already told, I think, about

00:08:43.055 --> 00:08:48.261
the subtle system
that is built in within us.

00:08:48.995 --> 00:08:51.397
This system has been built in

00:08:51.397 --> 00:08:54.400
during our evolutionary process.

00:08:56.736 --> 00:09:00.006
Whatever is the truth has to be tangible.

00:09:01.674 --> 00:09:06.212
It should not be accepted blindfolded
because I am telling you.

00:09:06.445 --> 00:09:12.985
You have to verify yourself that whatever
I'm telling you is the truth

00:09:13.286 --> 00:09:19.659
because you will have the actualization
of the experience of the truth.

00:09:20.660 --> 00:09:22.929
That is,

00:09:22.929 --> 00:09:24.664
firstly,

00:09:24.664 --> 00:09:27.667
that you are not this body, this mind,

00:09:30.036 --> 00:09:33.239
this ego, conditionings,

00:09:33.573 --> 00:09:37.209
but you are the pure spirit.

00:09:37.677 --> 00:09:40.680
This is the first truth about yourself.

00:09:41.347 --> 00:09:44.317
And the second one is that

00:09:45.217 --> 00:09:49.956
there is an all pervading
power of divine love,

00:09:50.523 --> 00:09:54.961
which they call by different names.
They may call it "Rūḥ."

00:09:54.961 --> 00:10:00.132
They may call it "God's Divine Love."
They may call it the Holy, the

00:10:00.933 --> 00:10:04.670
"Cool breeze of the Holy Spirit."

00:10:05.738 --> 00:10:11.210
They may call it "Paramchaitanya."
Call it by any name.

00:10:11.744 --> 00:10:14.747
But that is such a subtle

00:10:15.281 --> 00:10:18.284
force energy which exists,

00:10:18.351 --> 00:10:21.354
which does all the living work.

00:10:23.656 --> 00:10:25.958
Here now you see flowers.

00:10:26.258 --> 00:10:30.830
Flowers, so beautiful

00:10:30.863 --> 00:10:33.866
and we take them for granted.

00:10:34.200 --> 00:10:37.903
You don't question
how this miracle has taken place.

00:10:39.438 --> 00:10:42.174
Look at your eyes.

00:10:44.777 --> 00:10:50.816
We don't question how this camera
has come to exist.

00:10:51.417 --> 00:10:56.455
Look at your brain - what a computer it is.
You never question it

00:10:56.856 --> 00:11:00.893
how it has come to us,
how we have become human beings

00:11:01.193 --> 00:11:04.797
and how all these things are

00:11:07.199 --> 00:11:11.203
working within us automatically.

00:11:13.939 --> 00:11:16.942
If you ask who runs our heart,

00:11:17.410 --> 00:11:20.413
the doctors would say
it's an autonomous system.

00:11:21.080 --> 00:11:25.551
But if you go further and ask who is this "auto"?

00:11:26.152 --> 00:11:29.155
Who is running this heart?

00:11:29.755 --> 00:11:34.360
There are so many questions
which cannot be answered by science,

00:11:34.660 --> 00:11:37.663
and science is not conclusive.

00:11:38.130 --> 00:11:42.268
Recently, I was reading a book,
"The Limits of Science,"

00:11:43.002 --> 00:11:46.672
and he has asked
three questions in that book:

00:11:47.239 --> 00:11:52.678
"How do I come to be a human being?"
It's the first question.

00:11:53.145 --> 00:11:57.950
Second is: "What is the purpose of my life?"

00:11:58.584 --> 00:12:03.556
And (third): "Why should I live any longer?"

00:12:04.056 --> 00:12:09.161
All these three questions
can be very easily answered

00:12:09.695 --> 00:12:14.934
once you become the spirit.

00:12:18.270 --> 00:12:22.675
This transformation is also called
by many names.

00:12:23.042 --> 00:12:25.911
People call it "self-realization."

00:12:25.911 --> 00:12:28.581
Some call it "selfhood."

00:12:28.581 --> 00:12:31.550
Some say "self-knowledge."

00:12:31.550 --> 00:12:36.455
But what is this "self"
they are talking about and

00:12:36.689 --> 00:12:40.426
what will happen if we get the "selfhood"?

00:12:42.928 --> 00:12:47.833
I have to tell you, that all of you

00:12:48.167 --> 00:12:52.104
have got your divinity within yourself.

00:12:52.705 --> 00:12:58.144
And surprisingly, it is absolutely intact.

00:12:58.444 --> 00:13:02.381
Whatever you might have done,

00:13:02.648 --> 00:13:05.384
whatever mistakes
you might have committed,

00:13:05.384 --> 00:13:08.287
your divinity is absolutely intact.

00:13:08.287 --> 00:13:11.290
It is not at all disturbed, cannot be perished,

00:13:11.857 --> 00:13:17.296
cannot be perished, cannot be destroyed
by anything.

00:13:17.596 --> 00:13:20.332
The reason is:

00:13:20.666 --> 00:13:27.206
This Divinity is eternal,

00:13:27.406 --> 00:13:31.510
and whatever is eternal cannot be harmed.

00:13:31.844 --> 00:13:33.746
Nobody can destroy it.

00:13:33.746 --> 00:13:36.649
And that is within you there.

00:13:36.649 --> 00:13:39.819
And sometimes the glimpse of that
may be that

00:13:39.819 --> 00:13:45.057
you think whatever you see,
there must be something beyond.

00:13:45.291 --> 00:13:48.127
And when you start thinking that,
then you become

00:13:48.127 --> 00:13:52.765
a seeker of truth.

00:13:53.065 --> 00:13:56.302
Surprising, in these modern times,

00:13:56.535 --> 00:14:01.006
there are so many,
so many seekers of truth

00:14:01.540 --> 00:14:04.543
and so many are lost.

00:14:05.945 --> 00:14:08.948
When we start seeking truth,

00:14:09.982 --> 00:14:14.453
we definitely have to put faith into something.

00:14:14.753 --> 00:14:17.756
When we put our faith into religion also,

00:14:17.923 --> 00:14:21.160
what do we find that religion is

00:14:21.827 --> 00:14:24.830
power oriented or money oriented.

00:14:25.130 --> 00:14:28.133
So there is fundamentalism.

00:14:30.569 --> 00:14:33.572
Whatever attitude people might have taken

00:14:34.506 --> 00:14:37.142
those who started this religion

00:14:37.142 --> 00:14:40.446
are immaculate people, they are divine people

00:14:41.080 --> 00:14:45.951
and they were like the flowers
on one tree of spirituality.

00:14:46.552 --> 00:14:50.589
Only we have plucked these flowers
and we are fighting.

00:14:51.190 --> 00:14:54.193
How can we fight in the name of God?

00:14:55.427 --> 00:14:58.664
One should reason it out and once you reason it out,

00:14:58.664 --> 00:15:02.501
you start thinking:
"There must be something more to it."

00:15:02.868 --> 00:15:05.871
So when this..

00:15:06.939 --> 00:15:09.942
residual force, we call it as "Kundalini" in India.

00:15:10.242 --> 00:15:11.844
Kundalini means coils,

00:15:12.244 --> 00:15:14.280
starts rising,

00:15:14.280 --> 00:15:17.716
it passes through six centers

00:15:17.716 --> 00:15:21.320
and pierces through the seventh one,

00:15:22.721 --> 00:15:25.758
Which we call as "Brahmarandra"

00:15:25.758 --> 00:15:28.327
on the fontanel bone area,

00:15:28.427 --> 00:15:31.931
which was a soft bone in your childhood.

00:15:32.498 --> 00:15:35.734
And this opens.

00:15:37.836 --> 00:15:40.873
It is the actualization of your baptism.

00:15:40.906 --> 00:15:47.046
It is not just I put my hand on
your head and say: "Now you are baptized."

00:15:47.246 --> 00:15:51.517
This kind of self-certificate
is not going to help us.

00:15:51.784 --> 00:15:53.719
Now, if you become..

00:15:54.119 --> 00:15:58.324
say, the governor of this place,
then you have certain powers.

00:15:58.624 --> 00:16:03.128
Now, if you become the self
or if you become the self realized soul,

00:16:03.395 --> 00:16:05.864
then you must have some powers.

00:16:06.131 --> 00:16:08.033
And..

00:16:08.334 --> 00:16:13.539
people, normally,
certify themselves as this and that.

00:16:14.006 --> 00:16:17.142
This is not the way
you can achieve that state.

00:16:17.309 --> 00:16:22.114
You have to be honest,
because if you are honest seekers,

00:16:22.748 --> 00:16:25.250
then you should expect

00:16:25.250 --> 00:16:27.553
the actualization of the experience,

00:16:27.553 --> 00:16:32.191
first thing, about which Thomas
has written in his treatise.

00:16:32.224 --> 00:16:36.595
I wish you could read the Gospel
of Thomas, in which he has clearly said

00:16:37.129 --> 00:16:39.832
that the experience of self-realization

00:16:39.832 --> 00:16:43.802
is the most important thing,
and that it's to be achieved.

00:16:44.670 --> 00:16:47.673
You must be knowing Thomas ran away,

00:16:47.873 --> 00:16:50.809
because I think Paul
was trying to dominate him

00:16:50.809 --> 00:16:52.611
or whatever it was,

00:16:52.611 --> 00:16:54.747
and ultimately he went to India.

00:16:54.747 --> 00:16:59.284
But before going there, he went to Egypt
and he put all his treatise in a jar.

00:16:59.685 --> 00:17:01.887
For 50 years

00:17:01.887 --> 00:17:06.058
they have been trying to put it in
common language.

00:17:06.058 --> 00:17:09.061
And now the book is out, partly.

00:17:09.561 --> 00:17:12.798
So, this experience..

00:17:14.533 --> 00:17:18.103
has to be there, that you feel your spirit

00:17:20.039 --> 00:17:23.042
and feel this all pervading power

00:17:23.709 --> 00:17:25.044
all around us.

00:17:25.044 --> 00:17:27.946
So far, you have not felt it.

00:17:27.946 --> 00:17:30.215
So we have to be

00:17:30.215 --> 00:17:31.850
humble about it.

00:17:31.850 --> 00:17:34.853
As Christ has said, meek in heart

00:17:35.687 --> 00:17:37.956
will inherit the earth.

00:17:37.956 --> 00:17:40.959
That's a fact.

00:17:41.660 --> 00:17:44.630
You have to be meek about it that

00:17:44.630 --> 00:17:51.503
so far we have not found the truth
and that this divinity is within us,

00:17:52.271 --> 00:17:55.808
which is going to connect us to that

00:17:55.808 --> 00:17:58.777
all pervading power by which

00:17:59.011 --> 00:18:02.014
we are going to know the truth.

00:18:02.414 --> 00:18:05.317
Apart from

00:18:05.317 --> 00:18:08.120
many other

00:18:08.120 --> 00:18:09.321
benefits that

00:18:09.321 --> 00:18:12.724
you get by the awakening of this force within you.

00:18:14.226 --> 00:18:17.229
One, your physical

00:18:18.530 --> 00:18:20.632
conditions improve.

00:18:20.632 --> 00:18:23.435
Once you come to Sahaja Yoga,

00:18:23.435 --> 00:18:26.605
you are amazed
how your diseases are improved.

00:18:26.672 --> 00:18:30.209
Here in Cincinnati,
one lady who was suffering from cancer

00:18:30.209 --> 00:18:31.977
got cured.

00:18:31.977 --> 00:18:35.247
But curing people is a funny job.

00:18:35.948 --> 00:18:38.851
Once you cure them, they just disappear.

00:18:38.851 --> 00:18:40.352
They're very happy, they write to you:

00:18:40.352 --> 00:18:43.155
"Thank you very much, you cured us."

00:18:43.155 --> 00:18:46.859
But they're not the ones
who give light to others.

00:18:47.259 --> 00:18:50.262
Secondly,
mentally, people improve very much.

00:18:50.796 --> 00:18:53.465
All the habits

00:18:53.465 --> 00:18:56.468
which are destructive,
which we have acquired

00:18:56.902 --> 00:18:59.004
in anyway.

00:18:59.004 --> 00:19:02.007
They disappear and disappear

00:19:02.608 --> 00:19:04.409
so fast,

00:19:04.409 --> 00:19:07.179
that I have known people in England

00:19:07.179 --> 00:19:10.149
that overnight

00:19:10.149 --> 00:19:13.352
they gave up drugs, overnight.

00:19:15.087 --> 00:19:18.357
Today they are beautiful people,
professionals, working very well.

00:19:18.357 --> 00:19:20.826
This, I'm telling you

00:19:20.826 --> 00:19:23.829
in the year 1970 was happening

00:19:24.696 --> 00:19:26.098
in England.

00:19:26.098 --> 00:19:29.134
Or say '74, especially,

00:19:29.501 --> 00:19:33.038
in a big group, it happened.

00:19:34.706 --> 00:19:35.307
Then,

00:19:35.307 --> 00:19:38.310
the second advantage is that

00:19:39.178 --> 00:19:43.048
that you find your own spirit.

00:19:44.383 --> 00:19:48.253
Your spirit shines in your attention.

00:19:49.821 --> 00:19:52.824
Thus your attention becomes active.

00:19:54.593 --> 00:19:56.328
Like the light.

00:19:56.328 --> 00:19:58.597
Now there is a light here.

00:19:58.597 --> 00:20:01.400
When it falls on something
you can see it clearly,

00:20:01.667 --> 00:20:03.502
but it doesn't act on that.

00:20:03.502 --> 00:20:05.771
Maybe a little bit,

00:20:05.771 --> 00:20:10.709
it might, sort of spoil it,
but it doesn't act.

00:20:11.310 --> 00:20:14.313
But when your attention

00:20:14.746 --> 00:20:17.749
is enlightened,

00:20:17.849 --> 00:20:22.087
then wherever you put your attention, it acts

00:20:22.287 --> 00:20:25.290
that means on your hands also,

00:20:26.225 --> 00:20:28.794
you find this cool breeze blowing,

00:20:28.860 --> 00:20:30.796
and the fingertips,

00:20:30.796 --> 00:20:33.232
which are the sympathetic nervous endings,

00:20:33.232 --> 00:20:35.133
become enlightened.

00:20:35.133 --> 00:20:37.336
So five, six and seven.

00:20:37.336 --> 00:20:42.841
These centers on the left and the seven
centers on the right get enlightened

00:20:43.208 --> 00:20:47.179
and you immediately know
what's wrong with you.

00:20:47.346 --> 00:20:51.316
And also you can find out
what's wrong with others.

00:20:51.950 --> 00:20:55.988
So, what has happened to your attention is that

00:20:55.988 --> 00:20:58.991
you have got a new awareness

00:20:59.057 --> 00:21:02.060
where you become collectively conscious.

00:21:03.829 --> 00:21:05.497
Who is the other?

00:21:05.497 --> 00:21:08.467
When the microcosm becomes the macrocosm,

00:21:09.301 --> 00:21:12.971
when a drop becomes the ocean,
it becomes the ocean.

00:21:13.572 --> 00:21:16.575
In the same way, you start feeling

00:21:17.542 --> 00:21:19.878
the problems of other people,

00:21:19.878 --> 00:21:22.881
and you talk the language of centers.

00:21:24.583 --> 00:21:26.518
If you know how

00:21:26.518 --> 00:21:29.621
to cure your centers
and the centers of others,

00:21:30.656 --> 00:21:33.659
imagine what miracles you can do.

00:21:35.193 --> 00:21:38.130
If you see the problems of human beings,

00:21:38.130 --> 00:21:42.501
we can say ecological problems,
health problems, all kinds of problems

00:21:42.501 --> 00:21:45.170
we have.

00:21:45.170 --> 00:21:49.374
These are due
to fundamentally human beings

00:21:51.243 --> 00:21:54.246
and due to fundamentally, their centers.

00:21:55.113 --> 00:21:58.116
If you can put these centers right,

00:21:58.917 --> 00:22:01.720
you can put human beings right

00:22:01.720 --> 00:22:06.625
as well as you can put all the problems

00:22:07.659 --> 00:22:10.662
completely solved.

