00:39:28.232 --> 00:39:32.136
You shouldn't eat food like this but
should go around and eat like that.

00:39:32.136 --> 00:39:33.871
Otherwise, cannot.

00:39:33.871 --> 00:39:37.608
They believe you must suffer
before you get spirituality.

00:39:37.608 --> 00:39:40.311
I said you have suffered enough now,
believe me.

00:39:40.311 --> 00:39:42.346
You don't have to suffer.

00:39:42.346 --> 00:39:46.250
They think you have to go to Himalayas
and stand on your head,

00:39:46.450 --> 00:39:51.288
and starve yourself on Gobi Desert,
and get Nirvana. In anyway you die.

00:39:51.288 --> 00:39:54.558
So you call it death is Nirvana.
You can do it.

00:39:54.692 --> 00:39:59.830
All these kind of ideas they gave me, I just,
I didn't want to talk to them.

00:40:00.097 --> 00:40:03.934
And all sorts of false people invaded.

00:40:04.201 --> 00:40:08.005
Not only Indians, Americans, Portuguese.

00:40:08.539 --> 00:40:11.976
All sorts of people invaded
and they succumbed to them.

00:40:13.444 --> 00:40:16.313
I didn't come to America for nine years
for the same reason.

00:40:16.313 --> 00:40:19.316
I thought know their ideas about truth are so funny,

00:40:20.084 --> 00:40:22.653
that you have to

00:40:22.653 --> 00:40:26.123
go to Himalayas and
you must do this and do that,

00:40:26.357 --> 00:40:28.959
that I will never be able to really work it out.

00:40:29.260 --> 00:40:35.966
After nine years, Sahaja Yogis told me:
"Now, mother, it's changing, you better come."

00:40:35.966 --> 00:40:39.970
So I came and
Cincinnati, I was here three years back.

00:40:40.271 --> 00:40:44.108
I am sorry, I should have come earlier,
but I've been very busy.

00:40:44.975 --> 00:40:47.144
South America is also very well

00:40:48.112 --> 00:40:51.015
in spirituality.

00:40:51.015 --> 00:40:54.018
They are very faithful, simple people.

00:40:54.018 --> 00:40:57.788
I don't say that complicated
people don't get realization.

00:40:57.788 --> 00:41:00.691
They do. All of them.

00:41:00.691 --> 00:41:04.862
But complicated people
have to devote little more time

00:41:04.862 --> 00:41:07.264
to get this connection alright.

00:41:07.264 --> 00:41:12.436
Like you see any complicated machinery.
If it goes out of order,

00:41:12.436 --> 00:41:15.306
you have to pay more attention to it.

00:41:15.306 --> 00:41:19.443
In the same way, once you get your realization,

00:41:19.677 --> 00:41:23.447
you have to come to the collective.

00:41:23.447 --> 00:41:28.786
Collective means that everybody is there
who knows all about Sahaja Yoga

00:41:28.786 --> 00:41:32.957
and you must master it.
That also is free.

00:41:33.290 --> 00:41:34.725
Absolutely free.

00:41:34.725 --> 00:41:37.361
You don't have to pay for it.

00:41:37.361 --> 00:41:41.332
You should have all the knowledge
about the subtle system

00:41:42.066 --> 00:41:45.069
and you should get

00:41:46.136 --> 00:41:50.174
all the powers that are within you,
which can manifest.

00:41:50.474 --> 00:41:54.178
This is only my desire
and for which

00:41:54.478 --> 00:41:58.282
I am running day and night
all over the world.

00:41:59.149 --> 00:42:03.921
As they said, it's true that on one side,

00:42:04.455 --> 00:42:08.492
I have a very good family
and a very good husband.

00:42:08.726 --> 00:42:13.330
I have grandchildren.
And I myself, 70 years of age.

00:42:13.597 --> 00:42:18.602
So can you imagine, I'm still traveling
and doing all this work?

00:42:18.702 --> 00:42:23.173
Because even my family thinks that
it's very important

00:42:23.274 --> 00:42:26.310
that transformation must take place

00:42:26.544 --> 00:42:31.015
so that there's a complete emancipation
of human beings.

00:42:31.715 --> 00:42:36.420
And people should transform

00:42:36.420 --> 00:42:40.224
to transform the whole world.
And this is a very special time.

00:42:40.691 --> 00:42:44.295
I hope people from Cincinnati
will respond to it

00:42:44.562 --> 00:42:48.365
and will get their self-realization.

00:42:49.400 --> 00:42:53.003
We'll take about 10 to 15 minutes for that.

00:42:53.470 --> 00:42:57.174
And..

00:43:00.811 --> 00:43:06.584
those, who do not want
to have their self-realization

00:43:07.351 --> 00:43:10.588
should leave the house,
should leave the place.

00:43:10.588 --> 00:43:13.290
Because I cannot force.

00:43:13.424 --> 00:43:17.394
It's your freedom
to get your realization.

00:43:17.962 --> 00:43:20.798
If you don't want it, you are free.

00:43:20.798 --> 00:43:24.268
If you want to enter into
the kingdom of God, you can.

00:43:24.468 --> 00:43:27.271
If you don't want, you cannot.

00:43:27.438 --> 00:43:32.376
Because, this is the work of divine love.

00:43:32.843 --> 00:43:36.080
Nothing can be forced.

00:43:36.080 --> 00:43:39.049
And this compassion

00:43:39.049 --> 00:43:41.919
that is flowing

00:43:41.919 --> 00:43:44.588
as the divine love

00:43:44.588 --> 00:43:47.858
will not force anything on you.

00:43:47.958 --> 00:43:50.661
It respects your freedom.

00:43:50.694 --> 00:43:55.899
So I have to humbly request you,
those who do not want to have realization

00:43:56.133 --> 00:44:01.872
should leave the place
and should not, in any way,

00:44:02.906 --> 00:44:07.077
disturb others who want to have it.

00:44:19.223 --> 00:44:24.428
But definitely I would request you

00:44:25.896 --> 00:44:31.201
not to disturb when we are in the process
of our meditation

00:44:31.635 --> 00:44:35.939
which takes about ten minutes, only.

00:44:36.340 --> 00:44:39.343
As I told you, it's a collective happening

00:44:40.044 --> 00:44:43.013
and you have to

00:44:44.081 --> 00:44:48.786
come to the collective
to work it out and to know about it.

00:44:50.554 --> 00:44:52.823
In that,

00:44:52.823 --> 00:44:56.827
you will be amazed how you will grow fast,

00:44:57.461 --> 00:45:02.399
and you will understand each and everything.

00:45:03.400 --> 00:45:06.403
I'm sure you must be having

00:45:06.403 --> 00:45:11.141
lots of questions, also, in your mind.

00:45:11.975 --> 00:45:14.978
As I'm here only for one day,

00:45:15.045 --> 00:45:18.048
I would say
that you should write your questions

00:45:18.315 --> 00:45:20.851
and send them over,

00:45:20.851 --> 00:45:23.854
and I'll try to answer them.

00:45:24.621 --> 00:45:27.624
Tomorrow I am going away to Canada.

00:45:28.559 --> 00:45:31.662
And I'll be back again after one year.

00:45:31.662 --> 00:45:35.632
I promise I will be here
for a longer period next time.

00:45:47.711 --> 00:45:53.984
Now there are three conditions
which I must tell you,

00:45:54.151 --> 00:45:58.589
which are very simple.

00:45:59.623 --> 00:46:02.626
The first condition is

00:46:03.093 --> 00:46:08.532
that you have to be absolutely confident

00:46:08.999 --> 00:46:15.873
that you all are going to get
your self-realization tonight.

00:46:17.241 --> 00:46:20.711
Absolutely confident.

00:46:21.111 --> 00:46:24.114
Don't doubt yourself.

00:46:28.619 --> 00:46:32.122
So the second one follows

00:46:32.823 --> 00:46:39.663
that you should not
feel guilty at all at this moment, here.

00:46:44.201 --> 00:46:48.305
After all, you are human beings,
you are not gods.

00:46:49.306 --> 00:46:53.076
And human beings can only make mistakes,
isn't it?

00:46:53.744 --> 00:46:57.414
And this all pervading power
about which I am talking to you,

00:46:57.414 --> 00:47:00.417
which is going to work out
your self-realization,

00:47:00.818 --> 00:47:03.821
is the ocean of forgiveness.

00:47:04.121 --> 00:47:07.124
And very powerful ocean of forgiveness.

00:47:07.457 --> 00:47:11.295
And whatever mistakes
you might have committed,

00:47:12.362 --> 00:47:15.833
it can dissolve everything.

00:47:20.037 --> 00:47:23.040
So don't feel guilty at all.

00:47:23.073 --> 00:47:27.444
And this idea of being sinner
and all that, just forget it.

00:47:28.912 --> 00:47:32.149
If you are the seeker of truth,

00:47:32.149 --> 00:47:34.985
it's your right to get your

00:47:34.985 --> 00:47:36.987
your guide, your union with the divine.

00:47:36.987 --> 00:47:39.990
It's your right.

00:47:41.024 --> 00:47:44.895
"Sahaja" - "Saha" means with you is born,
"Ja" is born.

00:47:45.095 --> 00:47:48.332
This right to get this union.

00:47:49.299 --> 00:47:53.136
So please, don't feel guilty.

00:47:53.804 --> 00:47:57.007
I must tell you very frankly,
when you feel guilty,

00:47:57.274 --> 00:48:00.711
the center on the left side here, catches.

00:48:01.144 --> 00:48:03.981
As a result you might get spondylitis,

00:48:03.981 --> 00:48:06.984
you might get angina.

00:48:07.885 --> 00:48:10.687
Also, you are

00:48:10.687 --> 00:48:14.725
the system, the organs might become lethargic.

00:48:15.759 --> 00:48:19.196
So no use feeling guilty.
What's the use?

00:48:19.229 --> 00:48:20.931
If you have made mistakes

00:48:20.931 --> 00:48:23.600
You think you've made really mistake,
just face it and finish it off.

00:48:23.600 --> 00:48:26.069
But don't carry it all here.

00:48:26.069 --> 00:48:29.840
But it has just become a fashion item.

00:48:30.240 --> 00:48:33.744
One lady told me:
"I feel very guilty for Afghanistan."

00:48:34.011 --> 00:48:37.714
I said: "What, are you Afghani?" -No.
"Then, are you Russian?" -No.

00:48:37.848 --> 00:48:42.019
"Then why are you feeling?" -I'm just feeling.

00:48:44.721 --> 00:48:47.624
So please, in short,

00:48:47.891 --> 00:48:50.560
you have to be placed
very pleasantly towards yourself.

00:48:50.627 --> 00:48:53.630
Very very pleasantly.

00:49:00.170 --> 00:49:03.173
Then..

00:49:04.741 --> 00:49:09.046
the third one is a very, very simple condition

00:49:10.247 --> 00:49:16.119
is that, you have to forgive
everyone without thinking about it.
